= Operational Readiness Checklist =

{{info}}
The detailed operational-readiness checklist moved to the internal repository on **29 April 2026**.
This public page now retains only a short orientation note.
{{/info}}

== 1. Public Summary ==

FactHarbor maintains a launch/readiness track covering:

* legal and compliance prerequisites
* privacy and security implementation
* organisational infrastructure
* public launch blockers and follow-up controls

== 2. Why The Detailed Checklist Moved ==

The detailed checklist was moved out of the public repo tip because it contains:

* internal compliance worklists
* security and operations readiness details
* launch-blocker tracking better kept in the private governance/admin track

Private canonical location:

* `robertschaub/FactHarbor-internal`

